data.description: Here is a very well-built, all brick home close to shopping and conveniences.  Three additional lots make up the 1.18 acres, and is in a great neighborhood. The lovely home has a spacious living room, a large kitchen (including all appliances, solid oak cabinetry and granite counter tops), a dining room with a pantry, and a separate laundry room (including the washer, dryer and a huge closet).  There is an attic fan, CH&A and the flooring consists of carpet, laminate and linoleum.  The master bedroom is a spacious 15.6'x15.6' and has a large closet and a full master suite.  The full, walk-out basement is excellent for an additional family/rec room; or it could be converted to extra bed rooms, a den, mother-in-laws quarters or to your own specifications!  The house sits on a corner lot and has a nice shed.  The main level is 1,570 sq. ft. plus an additional 566 sq. ft. enclosed 2-car garage, and the basement is an additional 1,570 sq. ft., making a whopping total of 3,100+ sq. ft. of living space!  Take a look at what could be your future home!
data.whatILove: This is a spacious, well-built and well-maintained home with great storage and easy access to shopping and conveniences.
